    public class ElectricMeterElectricitySILModel
extends ElectricMeterElectricityModel
    The class ElectricMeterElectricitySILModel defines the SIL simulation model for the electric meter electricity consumption.

    Description

    Compared to the MIL model, this model uses the reference to the ElectricMeter passed as a run time simulation parameter to set the total power consumption in the corresponding variable in the component. Hence, the sensor method in the component will just have to return the latest value stored in the variable.
